longBusinessSummary: Mynaric AG, a laser communication company, engages in developing and manufacturing laser products for long-distance wireless data transmission between moving objects for terrestrial, airborne, and space applications in Germany and internationally. It offers CONDOR flight terminal, which is used in air-to-ground, air-to-air, space, ground-to-ground, and other applications. The company is also involved in the development, manufacture, sale, and operation of communication network equipment, software, systems and solutions, and related products. Its products provide connectivity solutions to link aircraft, unmanned aerial vehicles, high altitude platforms, satellites, and the respective ground stations. The company was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Gilching, Germany.
